    Scope and Contents
THE JEWISH EXPERIENCE PROJECT
James E. Myers, journalist and writer, discusses the Jewish community in Springfield; family, education, and religion; Springfield in the late 19th and early 20th centuries; anti-Semitism; and Temple B'rith Sholom.1 tape, 60 mins., 37 pp.
Interview by Syma Mendelsohn, 1973
